WEBVTT

00:00:29.363 --> 00:00:31.531
Prema scenariju Wachowskog,

00:00:31.531 --> 00:00:34.198
probuđeni čovjek mora se samo povezati

00:00:34.198 --> 00:00:37.576
i hakirati neon binarni kod Matrixa

00:00:37.576 --> 00:00:39.713
kako bi naučio kako letjeti helikopterom

00:00:39.713 --> 00:00:40.989
u sekundi.

00:00:41.409 --> 00:00:43.058
Ili ako ste Odabrani,

00:00:43.058 --> 00:00:44.328
ili jedan od Odabranih,

00:00:44.328 --> 00:00:46.099
ni ne treba vam helikopter,

00:00:46.099 --> 00:00:48.628
samo trebate par sunčanih naočala.

00:00:49.148 --> 00:00:51.916
Cerigradske mačke mogu 
žonglirati vlastitim glavama.

00:00:51.916 --> 00:00:54.095
iPadi su rudimentarni.

00:00:54.095 --> 00:00:56.058
Nijedan meč Metloboja ne može završiti

00:00:56.058 --> 00:00:58.681
dok se ne uhvati zlatna zvrčka.

00:00:58.681 --> 00:01:01.128
I odgovor na najvažnije pitanje života,